MAGUXDPS ;WOIFO/MLH - Imaging utility - rebuild ADTDUZ indices ; 6 Jun 2011 5:10 PM
 ;;3.0;IMAGING;**117**;Mar 19, 2002;Build 2238;Jul 15, 2011
 ;; Per VHA Directive 2004-038, this routine should not be modified.
 ;; +---------------------------------------------------------------+
